Glowing skin, the desi way ✨

Every time my skin feels dull or stressed, I go back to basics—straight to my kitchen. My go-to? A simple turmeric face mask that works like magic on acne, pigmentation, and tired-looking skin.

I mix wild Kasturi turmeric (no yellow stains, don’t worry!) with curd and a pinch of sandalwood. This combo not only soothes my skin but also helps reduce spots and evens out texture.

Turmeric’s anti-inflammatory & anti-bacterial nature makes it a staple in traditional skincare—and now, my self-care Sundays 🧡

I don’t get time every day (hello hectic schedule 👋), but I make it a point to treat my skin with this mask once a week. It’s my little skincare detox ritual.

Trust me, your skin will thank you.
